
Panel

  ╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │                                                        │
  │  Panel                                                 │
  │                                                        │
  │  Use Panel for rationale, release notes, and artifact  │
  │  context when one long identifier or timestamp needs   │
  │  to remain readable without blowing past the terminal  │
  │  width.                                                │
  │                                                        │
  │  Example values include                                │
  │  github.com/evanmschultz/hylla-fixture-go-2/pkg/very-  │
  │  long-artifact-reference/module and                    │
  │  run_2026-04-01T00:00:00.123456789Z_very_long.         │
  │                                                        │
  ╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
